# Vidsembly Design System

Use this rule for **any Vidsembly web property** (marketing site, free tools, insights/blog). Match the live reference: **https://tools.vidsembly.com**

Reference implementation repo: `Vidsembly-AI/free-tools` (especially `src/app/globals.css`, `Header`, `Footer`, `Hero`, `ToolCard`, `VidsemblyCta`).

## Brand

- **Voice:** Professional SaaS, creator-friendly, not salesy
- **Theme:** Dark only — do not introduce light mode or new color palettes unless explicitly requested
- **Logo:** `https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/66993e7ac009314a8eed947d/edbc980b-1a65-4d5b-b15e-23d235e8cb39/Main+Vidsembly+Logo+Gradient+%2B+White+PNG.png?format=1500w`
- **Font:** Jost (Google Font), applied site-wide via `--font-jost`

## Color Tokens

Define in Tailwind `@theme` or CSS variables — use these exact values:

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `background` | `#0a0a0f` | Page background |
| `surface` | `#12121a` | Cards, sections |
| `surface-elevated` | `#1a1a26` | Inputs, buttons, elevated panels |
| `border` | `#2a2a3d` | Card and section borders |
| `border-subtle` | `#1f1f2e` | Header/footer dividers |
| `foreground` | `#f4f4f8` | Primary text |
| `muted` | `#9494a8` | Secondary text, descriptions |
| `accent-blue` | `#3b82f6` | Links, category labels, hover accents |
| `accent-purple` | `#8b5cf6` | Gradient end, badges, hover accents |
| `accent-blue-soft` | `#1e3a5f` | Soft blue backgrounds |
| `accent-purple-soft` | `#2d1f4e` | Soft purple backgrounds (badges) |

## Utility Classes

Include in global CSS:

- `.gradient-text` — blue → purple gradient on headline emphasis words
- `.hero-glow` — radial blue/purple glow behind hero sections
- `.card-glow` — subtle gradient overlay on card hover

## Layout

- **Max widths:** `max-w-7xl` for page sections, `max-w-4xl` for tool/article content
- **Horizontal padding:** `px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`
- **Section spacing:** `py-10 sm:py-14` (content), `py-20 sm:py-28` (hero)
- **Responsive:** Mobile-first; nav collapses gracefully on small screens

## Components

### Header
- Sticky, `border-b border-border-subtle`, `bg-background/80 backdrop-blur-xl`
- Logo left; nav links right
- Nav link style: `text-sm font-medium text-muted`, hover → `bg-surface-elevated text-foreground`, `rounded-lg px-3 py-2`

### Hero
- Use `hero-glow` + optional subtle grid overlay (see `Hero.tsx` in free-tools)
- Headline: `text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight`
- Accent words: wrap in `<span className="gradient-text">`
- Subtitle: `text-lg sm:text-xl text-muted leading-relaxed`

### Buttons
- **Primary:** `rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-blue to-accent-purple px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-accent-purple/25 hover:brightness-110`
- **Secondary:** `rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface-elevated px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-foreground hover:border-accent-blue/50`

### Cards
- `rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 sm:p-6`
- Hover: `hover:border-accent-blue/40 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent-blue/5` (or purple variant for insights)
- Optional `card-glow` overlay on hover

### Badges
- Default: `rounded-full border border-border bg-surface-elevated text-xs text-muted`
- Accent ("Coming Soon", category): `border-accent-purple/30 bg-accent-purple-soft text-accent-purple`

### CTA block
- Centered card: `rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface px-6 py-10 text-center`
- Heading + short description + primary button linking to `https://www.vidsembly.com`
- Not intrusive — no popups, banners, or overlays

### Footer
- `border-t border-border-subtle bg-surface`, centered or split layout
- "Powered by Vidsembly" + link to vidsembly.com
- Include cross-links where relevant (e.g. Insights, Free Tools)

## Typography Scale

- Page title (h1): `text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight`
- Section title (h2): `text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold`
- Card title (h3): `text-lg font-semibold` or `text-sm font-semibold`
- Body: `text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed text-muted`
- Category label: `text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-accent-blue` or `text-accent-purple`

## Cross-Site Links

| From | Link to |
|------|---------|
| vidsembly.com | https://tools.vidsembly.com (Free Tools) |
| tools.vidsembly.com | https://www.vidsembly.com (product CTA) |
| Either | `/insights` on tools site when referencing guides |

## Do Not

- Introduce new color schemes, fonts, or light themes
- Add popups, cookie banners, chat widgets, or overlay modals unless explicitly requested
- Redesign existing Vidsembly pages unless the task asks for it
- Use generic Bootstrap/Material aesthetics — stay on-brand with dark + blue/purple

## When Building a New Vidsembly Site

1. Copy `globals.css` tokens from free-tools (or install shared tokens later)
2. Set up Jost via `next/font/google`
3. Reuse Header/Footer/CTA patterns above — adapt nav links per site
4. Compare side-by-side with https://tools.vidsembly.com before finishing
